* <span id="ref_buchanan">Buchanan, Patrick J. ''The Great Betrayal : How American Sovereignty and Social Justice Are Being Sacrificed...'' Little, Brown, 1998.</span>[[#Cold_War_era|(back)]]
* <span id="ref_carre">Carre, Jean Jacques ''French Economic Growth (Studies of economic growth in industrialized countries)'' Stanford University Press, 1975.</span>[[#Cold_War_era|(back)]]
* <span id="ref_collins">Collins, Robert M. ''More : The Politics of Economic Growth in Postwar America'' Oxford University Press, 2000.</span>[[#Cold_War_era|(back)]]
* <span id="ref_fingleton">Fingleton, Eamonn ''Unsustainable: How Economic Dogma is Destroying American Prosperity'' Nation Books, 2003.</span>[[#Cold_War_era|(back)]]
* <span id="ref_gardner">Gardner, H. Stephen ''Comparative Economic Systems (The Dryden Press Series in Economics)'' Dryden Press, 1988. [[#Cold_War_era|(back]]
* <span id="ref_gill">Gill, William J. ''Trade Wars Against America'' Praeger Publishers, 1990.</span>[[#Cold_War_era|(back)]]
* <span id="ref_lawrence">Lawrence, James ''Rise and Fall of the British Empire'' Little Brown & Co , 1995.</span>[[#Cold_War_era|(back)]]
* 《[[資本主義與自由|資本主義與自由]]》, 米爾頓·佛利民著，描述資本主義是最自由、公平、同時也是最可能達成平等的體制
* 《[[通往奴役之路|通往奴役之路]]》, [[弗里德里克·哈耶克|弗里德里克·哈耶克]]著，闡述集產主義和社會主義如何導致納粹控制德國。
* 《[[國富論|國富論]]》, [[亚当·斯密|亚当·斯密]]著，闡述資本主義的基礎，也是第一本將經濟學定義為一門學科的書籍。
* ''Capitalism: the Unknown Ideal,''（《資本主義：未知的理想》） [[艾茵·兰德|艾茵·蘭德]]著，主張純粹的資本主義是唯一道德的社會制度。

